txt.en: You have removed several of the Uruk-hai weapons from the possession of the enemy.
The Uruk-hai rebels have carelessly left their weapons strewn about the cave they have inhabited. Removing the weapons from the cavern would make things much more difficult for the enemy force.
You have removed the weapons of a great many Uruk-hai, making it improbable for the forces here to ever mount an attack against the Rohirrim.

The Uruk-hai rebels have stored their equipment throughout a cave they have inhabited in the Norcrofts. The weapons have been casually strewn about, and could be removed before they are weilded by their owners.
Take Uruk-hai swords from the cave
The Uruk-hai rebels are located in a cave, west of Caddabrand's camp.\n\nThe Uruk weapons have been carelessly left throughout the cave, leaving them ripe for removal.
